00:00:18.713 --> 00:00:28.864
I have to be careful what I say on this platform because YouTube censors things, so I have to flow with what I feel I can say.

00:00:28.865 --> 00:00:35.018
Right now, we stopped one. Ladies and gentlemen, we're doing it; it's working.

00:00:35.019 --> 00:00:43.878
Of course it's working—the power and the authority of the believer works—but there's fruit. There is fruit in what we're doing.

00:00:43.879 --> 00:00:51.506
There was a terrorist guy caught who had come across the border, and it was on all the news outlets.

00:00:51.507 --> 00:00:57.555
This guy lives two or three miles from my mom and dad's ranch.

00:00:57.556 --> 00:01:10.254
I told you they work for a guy raising Longhorn cattle. It's awesome because this guy had all kinds of plans.

00:01:10.255 --> 00:01:17.559
My brother is part of the sheriff's department, on the SWAT team, and works with law enforcement.

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:28.853
