00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:12.404
He had all kinds of AK-47s and everything; he was ready to do something.

00:02:12.405 --> 00:02:18.737
I don't know if it was a group of guys or whatever, but all I want to tell you all is that prayer changes things.

00:02:18.738 --> 00:02:25.500
We have power and authority as believers to pray and bind things up.

00:02:25.501 --> 00:02:32.286
We don't have to have that going on in our neighborhoods, in our churches, or our community.

00:02:32.287 --> 00:02:38.817
Jesus came and gave us power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:02:38.818 --> 00:02:44.706
I just want to encourage you all today because we are making a difference.

00:02:44.707 --> 00:02:53.243
Our little prayer group here of 50,000 or 60,000 people—we're doing something.

00:02:53.244 --> 00:03:02.594
That's a huge coliseum full of people praying, and I just want to encourage you all today about it. Now, I thought we'd take communion together.

00:03:02.595 --> 00:03:16.759
I'll wait a little bit if you want to get your communion and pray with me, but I just want to enter into worship and thank the Lord for all that he's done and all he's going to do.

00:03:16.760 --> 00:03:26.661
I know the enemy is not done. There's more coming; there's more coming in the name of Jesus.

00:03:26.662 --> 00:03:29.692
There's more uncovering coming; there's more exposing coming.

00:03:29.693 --> 00:03:37.167
And the Lord told me we're going to pray over Coachella again, this Trump rally that's coming on Saturday.

00:03:37.168 --> 00:03:51.942
We're going to pray over that. We're going to pray over the voting—no fraudulent behavior, all kinds of stuff. We're going to take authority over this hurricane.

00:03:51.943 --> 00:04:02.978
Some people say, "Oh, that's the hand of God; that's judgment,"but I don't believe God is bringing weather to judge Florida.

00:04:02.979 --> 00:04:16.299
If you believe that, that's on you, but the Bible says that the thief comes to kill, steal, and destroy, but God has come that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:04:16.300 --> 00:04:30.213
He's not out there killing, stealing, and destroying—that's the devil's job. The devil and God are not buddying up.

00:04:30.214 --> 00:04:40.036
God is a good God, and he is faithful and able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:04:40.037 --> 00:04:49.127
Let's get on God's side about things. This is the God of the New Testament. God is a God of mercy and love.

00:04:49.127 --> 00:04:59.166
Yes, there's a shaking to awaken, and yes, we open the doors for the enemy to do things because we open the doors to sin.

00:04:59.167 --> 00:05:12.820
Seedtime and harvest are accelerating, and it's not God doing it; it's immoral behavior that opens the door and says, "Come on, Mr.

00:05:12.821 --> 00:05:20.891
Devil, come in here and mess with me."God wants to show mercy; that's why he's saying pray.

00:05:20.892 --> 00:05:28.209
If he didn't want us to stop this, why would he want you to pray and then allow it to happen?

00:05:28.210 --> 00:05:33.528
That's boneheaded. God says, "I want you to stop this stuff.

00:05:33.529 --> 00:05:45.394
I'm bringing you on here to change things."I just want to encourage you all to get on the right side of things.

00:05:45.394 --> 00:05:53.781
We believe that God is a God of restoration and wanting to fix things.

00:05:53.782 --> 00:05:59.119
Like I said, whatever the devil means for bad, God is going to turn around for good.

00:05:59.120 --> 00:07:04.184
If something bad does happen in the natural, we'll pray good out of it. Let's pray that God turns it for good.

00:07:04.185 --> 00:07:17.872
The devil is an idiot, but I told you things were going to accelerate—the birthing pains, the labor pains.

00:07:17.873 --> 00:07:37.714
I told you when we passed Rosh Hashanah—I hope I didn't butcher that—the Lord said it would be a time of great acceleration with the weather, signs in the heavens, earthquakes, and wars and rumors of wars.

00:07:37.714 --> 00:07:47.697
The Lord said, "Brandon, it's going to increase by three times now."And look at what's happening; it's increasing and increasing.

00:07:47.698 --> 00:07:56.840
It's going to keep getting that way all through this next year, but glory to God, the light is going to get lighter and the dark will get darker.

00:07:56.841 --> 00:08:13.038
We aren't focused on the dark; we're focused on the light. We're focused on Jesus.

00:08:13.039 --> 00:08:25.934
Father, I'm going to enter into your throne by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of my testimony. I thank you for your body that was broken for me.

00:08:25.935 --> 00:08:55.174
You were wounded for my transgressions and bruised for my iniquities; the chastisement of our peace was upon him, and with his stripes, we are healed. Christ has redeemed me from the curse of the law.

