Now Lord, we take this blood and we apply the blood of Jesus over all our circumstances.

00:09:45.830 --> 00:09:57.814
This cup represents his blood, and it washes us from all our sins and all unrighteousness.

00:09:57.815 --> 00:11:06.760
We apply the blood over our house and our children. It makes us white as snow so I can come boldly before your throne.

00:11:06.761 --> 00:11:17.073
I take daily communion and I say, "Father, I come before your throne boldly,"and he says, "Welcome back, Brandon.

00:11:17.074 --> 00:11:38.267
