00:11:38.268 --> 00:12:16.020
Now we just give him praise. Thank you, Lord, that we enter into your throne by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony. Thank you, Jesus, that I'm healed and you set me free.

00:12:16.021 --> 00:12:44.198
Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief but was strong in faith, giving glory to God, fully persuaded that what God had promised he was able also to perform.

00:12:44.199 --> 00:13:04.030
It's time for overflow, ladies and gentlemen. We're going to believe God that more terrorists are exposed, that there is a covering, and that there are no mass shootings.

00:13:04.031 --> 00:13:11.824
I've told you we're going to pray over Coachella right now. So Father, in the name of Jesus, we come boldly before you.

00:13:11.825 --> 00:13:33.075
